00:00:46.790 --> 00:00:51.551
on your desk, you know, browsing these files. And the protocol http that we are

00:00:51.551 --> 00:00:53.936
speaking is, is just a very simple protocol that your

00:00:53.936 --> 00:00:57.291
browser uses to communicate with these servers. We'll discuss each of

00:00:57.291 --> 00:00:59.610
these pieces. Well, we won't spend a whole lot of

